      <p style={{fontSize:12,color:C.wn,margin:"0 0 4px",fontWeight:600}}>⏱ {elapsed<24?elapsed+"h":Math.floor(elapsed/24)+"d "+elapsed%24+"h"} fuera de servicio</p>
